{
  "info": {
    "name": "رسالة الخيرية API v3 — Complete",
    "description": "## نظام إدارة رسالة الخيرية\n\n**الـ Modules:**\n- Auth — تسجيل، دخول، OTP، Refresh Token\n- Sponsorships — برامج الكفالة\n- Subscriptions — اشتراكات الكفالات\n- Payments — طلبات الدفع (VodafoneCash, InstaPay, Branch, Representative)\n- InKindDonations — التبرعات العينية\n- EmergencyCases — الحالات الحرجة\n\n**الأدوار:**\n- Donor → يدخل برقم الهاتف\n- Reception → يدخل بالـ Username\n- Admin → يدخل بالـ Username\n\n**المتغيرات:**\n- `{{baseUrl}}` — http://resala.runasp.net\n- `{{token}}` — JWT Token (يتحفظ تلقائياً)\n- `{{refreshToken}}` — Refresh Token (يتحفظ تلقائياً)\n\n**Flow الاشتراك:**\n1. GET /sponsorships → اختار كفالة\n2. POST /subscriptions → أنشئ اشتراك\n3. POST /subscriptions/{id}/submit-payment → قدم دفع\n4. Staff reviews via /subscriptions/payments/pending\n5. POST /subscriptions/payments/{id}/verify → تأكيد",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://resala.runasp.net", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth — Public",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register — تسجيل متبرع جديد",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ahmed Mohamed\",\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"phoneNumber\": \"01012345678\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\",\n  \"job\": \"Software Engineer\",\n  \"landline\": \"0223456789\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "ينشئ حساباً للمتبرع ويرسل OTP على الإيميل.\n\n**Validation:**\n- phoneNumber: رقم مصري (01xxxxxxxxx)\n- password: 8 أحرف على الأقل + رقم\n- OTP صالح 10 دقائق"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم التسجيل", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": { \"userId\": 42, \"message\": \"تم التسجيل بنجاح. تحقق من بريدك الإلكتروني.\" },\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" },
            { "name": "409 - مسجّل مسبقاً", "status": "Conflict", "code": 409, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": false,\n  \"message\": \"رقم الهاتف مسجّل مسبقاً.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 409\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Email — التحقق من الإيميل",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-email", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","verify-email"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"847291\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "يتحقق من الـ OTP ويفعّل الحساب.\n**OTP**: 6 أرقام بالظبط"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم التحقق", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": \"تم التحقق من البريد الإلكتروني بنجاح. يمكنك تسجيل الدخول الآن.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" },
            { "name": "400 - OTP غلط", "status": "Bad Request", "code": 400, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": false,\n  \"message\": \"رمز OTP غير صحيح أو منتهي الصلاحية.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 400\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Donor) — دخول المتبرع",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var j=pm.response.json();","if(j.data&&j.data.token){","pm.collectionVariables.set('token',j.data.token);","pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken',j.data.refreshToken||'');","console.log('✅ Tokens saved. Role:',j.data.role);","}"], "type": "text/javascript" } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"phoneNumber\": \"01012345678\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "دخول المتبرع برقم الهاتف.\n✅ Token يتحفظ تلقائياً في `{{token}}`"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - دخول ناجح", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"message\": \"تم تسجيل الدخول بنجاح.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"dGhpcyBpcyBhIHNhbXBsZQ==\",\n    \"role\": \"Donor\",\n    \"userId\": 42,\n    \"name\": \"Ahmed Mohamed\",\n    \"phoneNumber\": \"01012345678\"\n  },\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" },
            { "name": "401 - بيانات غير صحيحة", "status": "Unauthorized", "code": 401, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": false,\n  \"message\": \"بيانات الدخول غير صحيحة.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 401\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin/Staff) — دخول الأدمن",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var j=pm.response.json();","if(j.data&&j.data.token){","pm.collectionVariables.set('token',j.data.token);","pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken',j.data.refreshToken||'');","console.log('✅ Token saved. Role:',j.data.role);","}"], "type": "text/javascript" } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@1234\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "دخول الأدمن أو الموظف بالـ Username.\n✅ Token يتحفظ تلقائياً"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - دخول ناجح (Admin)", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"dGhpcyBpcyBhIHNhbXBsZQ==\",\n    \"role\": \"Admin\",\n    \"userId\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Admin Resala\",\n    \"phoneNumber\": null\n  },\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot Password — طلب OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","forgot-password"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } }
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم إرسال OTP", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": \"تم إرسال رمز OTP على بريدك الإلكتروني.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset Password — إعادة تعيين الباسورد",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/reset-password", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","reset-password"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"847291\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecurePass456\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } }
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم التغيير", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": \"تم تغيير الباسورد بنجاح.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Resend OTP — إعادة إرسال OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/resend-otp", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","resend-otp"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"otpType\": \"EmailVerification\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "**قيم otpType:**\n- `EmailVerification`\n- `PasswordReset`"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم الإرسال", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": \"تم إرسال رمز OTP جديد.\",\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token — تجديد الـ Token",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var j=pm.response.json();","if(j.data&&j.data.token){","pm.collectionVariables.set('token',j.data.token);","pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken',j.data.refreshToken);","console.log('✅ Tokens renewed');","}"], "type": "text/javascript" } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh-token", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","refresh-token"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } }
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم التجديد", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"eyJhbGci...(NEW)\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"newRefreshToken==\"\n  },\n  \"statusCode\": 200\n}" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth — Staff & Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Donor by Staff — تسجيل متبرع (بدون OTP)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register-donor", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register-donor"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Mona Ali\",\n  \"email\": \"mona@example.com\",\n  \"phoneNumber\": \"01198765432\",\n  \"password\": \"TempPass123\",\n  \"job\": \"Teacher\",\n  \"landline\": \"0223456789\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "⚠️ يتطلب: Reception أو Admin Token"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": { \"userId\": 55, \"message\": \"تم تسجيل المتبرع بنجاح.\" }\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Staff — إنشاء موظف (Admin Only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/create-staff", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","create-staff"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Sara Hassan\",\n  \"username\": \"reception_sara\",\n  \"email\": \"sara@resala.org\",\n  \"phoneNumber\": \"01123456789\",\n  \"password\": \"StaffPass789\",\n  \"staffType\": 2\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "**staffType:**\n- `1` = Admin\n- `2` = Reception\n\n⚠️ يتطلب: Admin Token فقط"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم الإنشاء", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"data\": { \"staffId\": 3, \"username\": \"reception_sara\" }\n}" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "💝 Sponsorships — Public",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Sponsorships — كل برامج الكفالة",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sponsorships", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","sponsorships"] },
            "description": "متاح للجميع بدون Token"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - القائمة", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"كفالة يتيم\",\n    \"description\": \"برنامج لكفالة الأيتام\",\n    \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/resala/...\",\n    \"icon\": \"orphan-icon\",\n    \"targetAmount\": 50000,\n    \"collectedAmount\": 12000,\n    \"isActive\": true,\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-01T00:00:00\"\n  }\n]" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Sponsorship By ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sponsorships/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","sponsorships","1"] }
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - التفاصيل", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"كفالة يتيم\",\n  \"description\": \"برنامج لكفالة الأيتام\",\n  \"targetAmount\": 50000,\n  \"collectedAmount\": 12000,\n  \"isActive\": true\n}" },
            { "name": "404 - غير موجود", "status": "Not Found", "code": 404, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": false,\n  \"message\": \"برنامج الكفالة غير موجود.\"\n}" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "💝 Sponsorships — Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Sponsorship — إنشاء كفالة",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sponsorships", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","sponsorships"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"كفالة يتيم\",\n  \"description\": \"برنامج لكفالة الأيتام وتوفير احتياجاتهم الأساسية\",\n  \"imageUrl\": \"https://example.com/image.jpg\",\n  \"icon\": \"orphan-icon\",\n  \"targetAmount\": 50000\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "description": "⚠️ يتطلب: Admin Token"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "201 - تم الإنشاء", "status": "Created", "code": 201, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"كفالة يتيم\",\n  \"targetAmount\": 50000,\n  \"collectedAmount\": 0,\n  \"isActive\": true\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Sponsorship — تعديل كفالة",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sponsorships/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","sponsorships","1"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"كفالة يتيم — محدّث\",\n  \"description\": \"وصف محدّث\",\n  \"imageUrl\": \"\",\n  \"icon\": \"new-icon\",\n  \"targetAmount\": 75000,\n  \"isActive\": true\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } }
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم التعديل", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"كفالة يتيم — محدّث\",\n  \"targetAmount\": 75000\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Sponsorship — حذف كفالة",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sponsorships/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","sponsorships","1"] }
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "204 - تم الحذف", "status": "No Content", "code": 204, "header": [], "body": "" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📋 Subscriptions — Donor",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "⭐ Step 1: Create Subscription — إنشاء اشتراك",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/subscriptions", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","subscriptions"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sponsorshipId\": 1,\n  \"amount\": 500,\n  \"paymentCycle\": 1\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "**الخطوة 1:** إنشاء الاشتراك فقط.\n\nبعده استخدم `submit-payment` لتقديم الدفع.\n\n**paymentCycle:**\n- `1` = شهري\n- `3` = كل 3 شهور\n- `6` = كل 6 شهور\n\n⚠️ يتطلب: Donor Token"
          },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 - تم إنشاء الاشتراك", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": true,\n  \"message\": \"تم إنشاء الاشتراك بنجاح. يمكنك الآن تقديم طلب الدفع.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 5,\n    \"donorId\": 3,\n    \"donorName\": \"Ahmed Mohamed\",\n    \"sponsorshipId\": 1,\n    \"sponsorshipName\": \"كفالة يتيم\",\n    \"amount\": 500,\n    \"paymentCycle\": \"Monthly\",\n    \"status\": \"Active\",\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00\",\n    \"nextPaymentDate\": \"2026-05-24T00:00:00\",\n    \"createdOn\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00\",\n    \"recentPayments\": []\n  }\n}" },
            { "name": "409 - مشترك بالفعل", "status": "Conflict", "code": 409, "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}], "body": "{\n  \"succeeded\": false,\n  \"message\": \"أنت مشترك بالفعل في هذا البرنامج.\"\n}" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "⭐ Step 2A: Submit Payment (VodafoneCash) — دفع فودافون كاش",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/subscriptions/5/submit-payment", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","subscriptions","5","submit-payment"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "paymentMethod", "value": "1", "type": "text", "description": "1=VodafoneCash" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "500", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "senderPhoneNumber", "value": "01012345678", "type": "text", "description": "رقم المحوّل منه" },
                { "key": "receiptImage", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "صورة إثبات التحويل (jpg/png, max 5MB)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**الخطوة 2 - VodafoneCash/InstaPay:**\n\n- `paymentMethod`: `1`=VodafoneCash, `2`=InstaPay\n- `senderPhoneNumber`: رقم الهاتف المحوّل منه (01xxxxxxxxx)\n- `receiptImage`: صورة الإيصال (jpg/png, max 5MB)\n\n⚠️ يتطلب: Donor Token\n⚠️ Content-Type: multipart/form-data"
          },
          "response": [
